{"type":"text","timestamp":1778974752263,"sessionID":"ses_1ccd7b077ffeG5neEOCLcs0A6b","part":{"id":"prt_e33286c790010E5N326EBnWXly","messageID":"msg_e332864610015FRIujlWYXk6fy","sessionID":"ses_1ccd7b077ffeG5neEOCLcs0A6b","type":"text","text":"The issue is clear: create `vesicle membrane tethering activity` under `GO:0140177` and update the parent definition to mention vesicle. I’ll follow the GO checkout/checkin workflow, including term searches, design-pattern review, reference validation, ontology validation, and a local commit.","time":{"start":1778974747769,"end":1778974752260}}}
