{"type":"text","timestamp":1778975799023,"sessionID":"ses_1ccd7b077ffeG5neEOCLcs0A6b","part":{"id":"prt_e33384bce001hDSHqrNiU5z9D6","messageID":"msg_e333828b2001ua9TROiwDnuIdu","sessionID":"ses_1ccd7b077ffeG5neEOCLcs0A6b","type":"text","text":"Implemented and committed the issue #31863 work locally.\n\n**Commit**\n`d280957 Add tracker link for vesicle tether activity`\n\n**What changed**\nAdded the missing issue tracker metadata to `GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity`:\n\n```obo\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863\" xsd:anyURI\n```\n\nThe requested new term `GO:7770062 vesicle membrane tethering activity` and the updated parent definition including “vesicle” were already present in the local ontology.\n\n**Validation**\nPassed both before and after the change:\n\n`make -C src/ontology travis_build`\n\nReference validation also passed for the supporting excerpts in `RESEARCH.md`.\n\n**Created uncommitted files**\n`ISSUE_COMMENTS.md`\n\n`PR_COMMENTS.md`\n\nAlso created uncommitted support docs required by the workflow:\n\n`RESEARCH.md`\n\n`DESIGN_PATTERNS.md`\n\nThere are pre-existing/unrelated untracked or deleted files in the workspace; I did not commit or modify them.","time":{"start":1778975787982,"end":1778975799019}}}
